comment: Randolph (MEM) trips Durant (GSW) and affects his SQBR.
[Detectable with stop watch] Iguodala (GSW) is in the paint without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Durant (GSW) maintains legal guarding position on Randolph (MEM).
Green (GSW) makes incidental contact with Allen (MEM) that does not affect his SQBR.
Conley (MEM) maintains legal guarding position on the shot attempt by Curry (GSW).
Iguodala (GSW) and Allen (MEM) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Allen (MEM) and Thompson (GSW) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Allen (MEM) and Curry (GSW) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Daniels (MEM) obtains a legal guarding position outside of the restricted area on the driving shot attempt by Durant (GSW).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court (blocking foul) was overturned. Daniels (MEM) was outside of the restricted area and in a legal position.
[Detectable with stop watch] Gasol (MEM) is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
Daniels (MEM) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Curry (GSW) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Green (GSW) makes contact with Allen's (MEM) head on the rebound.
Thompson (GSW) makes marginal contact with Conley (MEM) that does not affect his SQBR.
Thompson (GSW) makes incidental contact with Conley (MEM) that does not affect his SQBR.
Allen (MEM) intentionally kicks the ball on the play.
Curry (GSW) commits a take foul on Martin (MEM).
